website_summaries.verdict: These waterproof covers work with prefold, fitted, flat, or contoured plain cloth diapers to hold in moisture while resisting stains. 5 covers per pack, and different patterns are available.
pros: Leg gussets contain the mess, while the hip snaps keep the covers comfortably fitted around baby's waist
Waterproof polyester is durable, pliable, and breathable
Size 1 fits babies from 6 to 18 lbs., while size 2 accommodates toddlers between 18 and 40 lbs
cons: Adorable, but a little pricey for diaper covers

customer_reviews.title: These work great. We've only had one diaper explosion that actually ...
customer_reviews.text: These work great. We've only had one diaper explosion that actually made it outside the cover. The only downside for me is that you're only going to get the full weight range of the sizing if you're using their inserts. I'm using prefolds me my little guy is only 3 months and will be grown out of size 1 VERY soon. The inserts are just too expensive though; one of the big reasons I did cloth was to save money.
customer_reviews.author: bookgrl

customer_reviews.title: These diaper covers and the osocozy diapers work perfectly together ...
customer_reviews.text: These diaper covers and the osocozy diapers work perfectly together. They are the only brand that I have tried and I am a first-time cloth diaper using mom.
customer_reviews.author: Private K.

customer_reviews.title: Great option
customer_reviews.text: Great covers. Easy to use. Easy to wash - although the elastic can stain (but staining should be expected, these are diapers after all). I do wish they had a lip at both ends to hold a prefold in place (like Cloth-Eez covers), but they work fine without it. I have had some wicking to the elastic if I don’t change my son quickly enough, but I’ve never had a blow out like with disposables. These hold in pee and poo really well, but I wouldn’t recommend going more than 3 hours. Make sure your diaper is fully tucked into the cover once it’s on & there should be no problem :)
customer_reviews.author: amia

Easier and quicker to change baby and better fit.. can see it wearing faster r/t washing ... Cloth diapers are the way to go! You save tons of money! customer_reviews.title: We love our Duos!

customer_reviews.title: Our Favorite Covers
customer_reviews.text: So far thirsties really are our favorite covers. They're holding up really well, and while I wasn't the biggest fan of the fact that they're multiple sizes initially, it has made it easier to keep her from just swimming in a giant diaper. We got our size ones second hand and they'd held up really well through one baby already and these are the new size twos that we bought. We're very happy with the lack of leakage, the snaps are durable, they wash well, and we've been able to sun bleach most of the stains out of them.

product_meta.title: Thirsties Package, Snap Duo Wrap, Outdoor Adventure Collection Birdie Size 1
product_meta.description: Size:Size One (6-18 Pound)| Color:BirdeHere at Thirsties, we're passionate about the Great Outdoors. Camping, hiking, simply basking in the breathtaking beauty - it's one of the things that make life great. Our new Outdoor Adventure Collection Package comes with 5 Duo Wrap Covers: 3 new nature-inspired prints and 2 solids. Thirsties Duo Wraps are completely waterproof yet remain breathable, pliable, and very comfortable for your baby's delicate skin. With the adjustable rise you will only need two sizes from birth to potty. Leg gussets provide advanced leak-proof protection and bindings are super-soft against your baby's skin. Whether your baby is tall or short, thin or chunky, this cover will keep those messes contained! Thirsties Duo Wraps are the preferred wrap for prefolds or trim fit diapers, such as our Stay Dry Duo Insert diaper. The inside of Duo Wraps can be wiped clean between uses allowing for fewer wraps in rotation and greater affordability. We recommend one cover for every 3-4 diapers in. We are very proud of the fact that all Thirsties products are manufactured in Colorado, USA, by a group of very talented individuals, many of whom are moms who work in the comfort and convenience of their own homes. Proudly manufactured in the USA.
feature_bullets: Outdoor Adventure Collection Package includes 5 Duo Wrap Covers: 3 prints and 2 solids
Pliable and breathable wraps provide an ultra-comfortable waterproof cover for fitteds, prefolds, flats and contoured diapers
For an easy to use all-in-two diaper, pair with our Stay Dry Duo Insert
Leg gussets for advanced leak protection
Wipe wrap clean between diaper changes. We recommend 1 wrap for every 3 to 4 diapers in rotation
